Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:09.47,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,是PIKAPIKAPOP啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.57,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是要幹什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:15.01,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要和這個品牌搞聯動合作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:16.58,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,商品模特哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:18.99,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:22.55,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是為了CD的宣傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:27.92,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 活動期間購物袋和店內BGM也都是凸RATION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:32.00,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,在CD的發售日前後  露出度越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.49,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,P君大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:34.08,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.54,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去告訴姐姐說 呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:37.89,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.87,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,製作人 好色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:41.33,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:46.30,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得小P說的是指面向媒體的上鏡程度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.43,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 是那方面呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.55,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,那方面？哪方面？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:53.67,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,米莉亞不懂這個也沒關係喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:57.59,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓我露多少都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.89,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,就按P君喜歡的來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:01.73,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.87,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,請容我回去探討一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.33,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 P君只會說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.30,charu,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:10.83,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好開心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:12.27,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在被戲弄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.46,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,配合聯動商品的發售 大家將參加相應的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.41,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,活動！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.26,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,Live？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,很可惜 因為場地的原因沒法唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:26.32,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,將是脫口秀的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.10,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 好土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:29.45,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,脫口秀是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:30.63,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:34.23,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聊些小秘密的話題 或是戀愛話題什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.28,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:38.78,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,要聊很害羞的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.18,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:42.79,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次○○的事情什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:44.89,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,○○？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.52,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,事前先討論一下要說的內容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:50.52,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:52.53,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:55.26,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,挺擔心的…
