Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.73,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話能拍一張嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:31.37,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,只拍琪拉莉好偏心 我也要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.85,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,照相機好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:36.12,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 難道你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.49,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.81,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,「凸RATION」首張單曲CD發售中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.70,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:44.83,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,快溜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:49.66,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,實在抱歉 你們兩個等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.25,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.80,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是真人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.95,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆不要突然就跑掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:06.58,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦 不過這時候不是該製作人出面解決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.05,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,P君？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:11.35,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 製作人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.97,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有偷拍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.36,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,你有把手機衝著女孩子拍攝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:20.74,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.24,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.09,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是製作人 這是名片…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.15,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 今早剛好用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.85,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:32.91,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,製作人迷路了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.72,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我打電話試試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.20,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我接下電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:42.26,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 讓你接的話你會刪除數據的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.42,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,P君沒有接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:48.63,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我給事務所打個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.24,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.33,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是灰姑娘企劃的新田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.16,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,千川千尋小姐在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.21,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:01.42,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.88,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,製作人現在好像在警察那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:06.83,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之摯友竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.41,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,發生事件了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:11.96,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那個 先打110
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:12.90,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.79,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,通話中…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:17.31,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.54,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐 姐姐 P君他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:21.70,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,哈啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.93,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:26.78,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我先走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.57,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？說好的卡拉OK怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.20,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:33.97,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:39.05,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,您撥打的電話現在不在服務區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.15,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 好像關機了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.83,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,小P怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:50.38,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  都怪我們跑開才走散的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:54.58,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,擁抱擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:59.75,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的 順著來的路找下小P吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:04.94,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近都是琪拉莉的院子哦 馬上就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:06.58,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.13,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.89,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 謝謝了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:22.29,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:28.16,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,美波 小P有回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.61,charu,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:34.39,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐在車站？ 嗯 那個 這是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:39.16,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 你們可以先來車站嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:44.46,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等下 琪拉莉說 P君在警察那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:45.31,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.50,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去警察那裡看看 掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:48.86,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…莉嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:52.89,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:56.44,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,去找她們 要找遍整個城嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.38,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒有跑多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:02.91,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下 現在還是不要漫無目的地亂走比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:04.39,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:08.85,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,要是等聯繫到的時候 跑到完全相反的方向了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.70,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,她們也不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:13.37,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:16.42,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,不在！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.32,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有來這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.01,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,警察那裡不是指警察局嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:24.76,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,通話中…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.93,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會留下記錄的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.05,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 P君究竟怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.49,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,小P剛才還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.31,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.71,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊找一邊去車站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.91,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐她也在車站 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.86,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,琪拉莉她有打過電話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.72,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.02,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,就在剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:52.31,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴她們你在警察那裡 應該是去找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.97,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:16:00.06,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 現在有人能來這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.09,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,又不在 真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.74,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,小P和美嘉在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:09.71,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.11,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,莉嘉 你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:12.65,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,在車站
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.47,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼去了車站 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.20,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不在原地不動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.81,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是姐姐你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.18,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有可是不可是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.44,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:22.74,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,米莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.01,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:26.77,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,莉嘉 莉嘉!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.37,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,莉嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.32,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能來幫忙真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.19,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有找到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.52,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 應該很快就會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.08,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果趕不上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.16,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,三位能幫忙應對下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:49.27,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.11,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,不費吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.94,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…難道要穿這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.20,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外還會有別的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.53,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,留在事務所看家就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.10,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.00,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.29,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:12.79,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,米莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:14.87,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:18.77,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,穿西裝的人看著都像小P對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.21,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,常有的常有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:23.93,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,下個活動要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.03,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要趕過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:26.71,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,那製作人怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:33.68,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很擔心 但放著粉絲們不管 小P才會更生氣ni
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:45.19,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,城崎小姐 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.21,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為你不好好看著莉嘉才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.63,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.63,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,你還問發生什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:55.48,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是製作人吧 要好好看著才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:56.67,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:18:00.14,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來 請看著我的眼睛說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.84,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐估計很生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:10.71,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,美嘉和小P肯定在會場等著的ni
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:13.25,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,現在趕緊去的話肯定還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:16.65,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個 琪拉莉衝刺！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.64,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 琪拉莉衝刺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.45,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 莉嘉你的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:27.31,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說一直是強忍著走過來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.19,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,想要漂亮是需要忍耐的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.69,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有創可貼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.22,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:35.99,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:40.24,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪琪拉莉帶著你們四處走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:45.41,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我沒說要去找小P而是待在原地的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:49.87,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果我沒說去吃可麗餅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.58,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,小P也不會迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.51,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,莉嘉和米莉亞 你們也不會像現在這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.20,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.18,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.17,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.11,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯 這不是琪拉莉的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.34,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腳 沒問題的 衝刺著去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:10.92,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.52,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 莉嘉 莉嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:18.79,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.33,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:26.52,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,琪拉莉 那個…你可以抱著莉嘉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:27.42,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.53,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒辦法衝刺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.00,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就開始表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.14,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就不算遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.00,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們三人超顯眼地 去吸引大家目光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.51,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,琪拉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.51,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,琪拉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:41.77,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:43.85,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.82,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,在通話中突然就掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.84,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後去車站找了 也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.31,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不知道該怎麼辦了
